The paper deals with image manipulation using natural language instructions, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) domains. The proposed system uses a neural network for image transformation, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the system involves text-based image retrieval, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
